{"tid":1284250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"可以用幾分鐘睇下嘅一篇文：美中攻防戰——香港國會普選","createTime":"2019-07-04T05:44:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T15:16:20.000Z","uid":138946,"like":121,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"98d2a13eb2c48e8df8081ff692203ef124be44cc","tid":1284250,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:44:09.000Z","msg":"轉載自Facebook專頁：敗傲籮即高 嘥仁時（Bio Sciences ）<br />\n<br />\n原post link：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/697033560746082?s=100013736653161&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F347501365699305%2Fposts%2F697033560746082%3Fs%3D100013736653161%26sfns%3Dmo&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=da4e5663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/347501365699305/posts/697033560746082?s=100013736653161&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美中攻防戰&mdash;&mdash;香港國會普選<br />\n<br />\n中共不是省油的燈，二十多年來中共一直不容許香港普選國會，現在兩日間突然透過不同人士發言談及政改普選。這個可能是以退為進的策略。<br />\n<br />\n因為美國的《香港人權與民主保證法案》將要通過，並且可能限定香港要於 2020 年進行國會普選。若等到該法案通過後，香港才重啓政改，這就必須乎合美國規定，中共沒有走動空間。而且，這就是香港遵從了美國的法案，便間接承認了美國擁有香港的管治權。<br />\n<br />\n因此，中共現在打算先行推動政改，製造一個類似普選的假東西，然後會有議員代表香港人接受。那麼就搶先在美國的法案通過前，使香港有「民主」，減低了美國的影響，也削弱了該法案的力量。同時，香港就會出現一群主張「袋住先」的人，大量輿論會導向接受中共的方案。之後，國會普選就沒有了，一切返回原狀，先烈的血白流，義士枉然被控⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n這次，是中共以退為進，香港人現在有兩個選擇。一、有法治守信用的美國法案；二、沒法律亂撒謊的中共引誘。而今次，是香港向美國求援的，道義上就該接受美國出手。若香港選錯了就萬劫不復。<br />\n<br />\n現在是中共疲弱之時，牠退讓一步，香港就要向前推進十步。這機會，是用血換來的，不容任何政棍代表香港放棄！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157231814597225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157231814597225%3Fs%3D600287265%26sfns%3Dmo&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=4b06b9e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157231814597225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157230744967225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157230744967225%3Fs%3D600287265%26sfns%3Dmo&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=f8985d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157230744967225?s=600287265&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"257af7edf34afd8a26de23728449faab553614a8","tid":1284250,"uid":138946,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"會唔會發生都好，我係覺得有必要警惕防備一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a84c73bee6bf03651397aeaf8375119b6505bfe","tid":1284250,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:47:07.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397354b0a746ec6bbc25a42412143742f0fdcc9c","tid":1284250,"uid":522,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"民建聯同泛民講既野都信唔過, 用普選既名義去包裝假普選"},{"pid":"7d756d7e32bdb22a67dc47dacab0319d2beab521","tid":1284250,"uid":138946,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"397354b0a746ec6bbc25a42412143742f0fdcc9c","tid":1284250,"uid":522,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:47:09.000Z","msg":"民建聯同泛民講既野都信唔過, 用普選既名義去包裝假普選"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"我係覺得今次部分泛民係醒目咗嘅，但醒唔醒到最後就另一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fbf482ce8901fd76e6cd56bac45d1ec7b999848","tid":1284250,"uid":138946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:50:07.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1c0f79f6d3e0258654b3923780ebfb33d86e5a","tid":1284250,"uid":18639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T05:53:10.000Z","msg":"絕對有發生既可能 大家要盡全力阻止"},{"pid":"d7071b1346cf8e3b5c1d91e4e3a1005dd2cb3083","