"2019-07-04T06:00:29.000Z","msg":"記住2014係反袋住先! 即係話只有一步到位其他都係伏!<br />\n<br />\nbtw篇野雲味濃"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T06:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢立場係偏雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢篇嘢確實有道理所以我放上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:01:53.000Z","msg":"佢係偏雲架<br />\n而且陳雲直情出左Post<br />\n<br />\n陳雲：共產黨主動談政改。緩兵之計而已，最多是合併工商界、取消漁農界，釋放十個功能組別之類。<br />\n共產黨示弱或示好的時候，正正就是香港人要加緊打擊他們的時候。不將共產黨在香港打翻在地，踩上一腳，他們不會當你是對手看待。<br />\n共產黨被逼打不還手的時候，就是要狠狠打他們的時候。打到他們吐出香港，給香港普選，完成自治。"},{"pid":"173c5439e3a0db767cc645c3171a0b96ebdaf5b2","tid":1284250,"uid":70332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:03:22.000Z","msg":"【專訪】曾鈺成：可考慮831框架外討論重啟政改<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=354086\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354086&d=3FM1mHFWgl829bPTLnnFI4HZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=60f56d0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D354086&h=52356821\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=354086</a><br />\n<br />\n放風探聽虛實啦<br />\n要醒定呀"},{"pid":"6ffced1187511af38d849bb063ba1873fc706aa3","tid":1284250,"uid":158317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GzfbXtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGzfbXtQ.png&h=dd2bba79&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f628601d6437cde87b8d454c45513dae92cfc273","tid":1284250,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ea8486f70467a707685fc6a37d8ee2ea5f87abb","tid":1284250,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa458d2ac0ee9615681a43ebe22b9493926b6fb8","tid":1284250,"uid":62749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86741b76c61d98bef11216c32b